Package: agriwater
Title: Agrometeorological Spatial Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Cesar de Oliveira Ferreira Silva
Maintainer: Cesar de Oliveira Ferreira Silva <cesaroliveira.f.silva@gmail.com>
Description: an R package for spatial modeling of energy balance and actual evapotranspiration using satellite images and agrometeorological data.
Options of satellite are: Landsat-8 (with and without thermal bands), Sentinel-2 and MODIS. Respectively spatial resolutions are 30, 100, 10 and 250 meters. User can use data from a single agrometeorological station or a grid of agrometeorological stations (using any spatial interpolation method).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: raster,
    sp,
    rgdal
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
